Introduction
==============

Django-social-auth-app utilize https://github.com/omab/django-social-auth, 
add template for login page, user edit page. And packs this up into single
url conf. So you need not do this setup everytime you build a new page.

Installation
==============

1. Clone the read-only repo

     git clone git://github.com/vencax/django-social-auth-app.git

2. Install the dependencies via PIP.

     pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Add socialauthapp into your INSTALLED_APPS as well as other dependant apps.

4. Include vxkforum.urls into your root url conf

     url(r'^auth/', include('socialauthapp.urls')),
		
5. You are done


